{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_09_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央 3話 頑固なマネージャーさん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "教えて。悩んでることが成長って……どういうこと？\nうじうじ悩んでる、私のどこが成長してるっていうのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tell me. What do you mean worrying is growth?\nWhich part of me‚ agonizing like this‚ is growing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.8619271915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。以前の莉央さんなら、こんな風に\n他人と自分の間で悩んだりはしなかったでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Rio-san in the old days\nwouldn’t have agonized over the opinions of others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "自信を持って\n自分の意見を通そうとしたんじゃないでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She would have confidently\npushed her own opinions‚ wouldn’t she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.9306794485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、LizNoirのスタイルはそうやって作って\n守ってきた。それが私達の強さだと思ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that’s how we built and maintained LizNoir's style.\nI thought that was our strength.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.466666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今はそれだけじゃダメだと思うの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ I don’t think that’s enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.111677456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.5308156809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "愛やこころを受け入れた時のように\n今までは思いもしなかった意見も取り入れようって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just like when we accepted Ai and Kokoro‚\nI thought we should be open to ideas we hadn’t",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そう思ってたんだけど……\nそれが正しいのかどうかも分からなくなってきてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "considered before‚ but…\nNow I’m not even sure if that was the right thing to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.1561889173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ダメね。ブレているのよ、今の私は\nこれじゃ、我を通すだけだった以前の私の方がマシよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is bad. I’m wavering.\nMaybe my old self‚ who only pushed her own way‚ was better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 54.9978018285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、我を通すのは強さでもあるけど\n弱さでもあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ being stubborn can be a strength‚\nbut it can also be a weakness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "どこに弱さがあるっていうの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean it's a weakness?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4014526051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 62.7697741113
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは、自分の枠から出ることが出来ない\n臆病さの裏返しでもあるからです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because it can also be a sign of being afraid\nto step outside of your comfort zone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だから今の莉央さんは成長の途中。俺はそう思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I believe you're in the midst of growing‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6593865635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 74.3341464283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "成長の途中、か。そんな風に考えたこと、なかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the midst of growing… huh? I’ve never thought about it that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3341464283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.1804726524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "今の私達に、勢いも実力も備わっているのは確かよ\nでもBIG4にはあと一歩、届かない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that we have both momentum and skill right now.\nBut we’re still one step away from reaching BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.5936664504
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4入りするためにもっと強くなりたい。勝ちたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to be stronger to get into BIG4. I want to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5936664504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "そのためにはどうすればいいのか、ずっと考えてる\n……このままじゃ、終われないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m always thinking about what I need to do to achieve that.\n…I can’t end it like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.4999913532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.4101450205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、いつもなら断ってもおかしくない仕事にも\n挑戦しようと思ったんですか？　莉央さんらしいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that why you decided to take on a job you normally\nwould have refused? That’s so like you‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6666534422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、これから私達はどうすればいいのか\nこのところ、ずっと迷っていたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks. As for what we should do from now on…\nI’ve been lost lately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5333201089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.1499642293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今の言葉で手がかりが掴めた気がする\n私達はもっと成長出来るはず。……いえ、してみせるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But your words just now gave me a clue.\nWe can grow even more. …No‚ we will grow even more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0666534422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.5466524999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺も他の仕事を調整して\n出来るだけ撮影現場に顔を出すようにします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll try to adjust my schedule and\nbe present at the filming site as much as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7333190916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "いいわよ、無理しなくても\n貴方が見るべきアイドルは、他にも沢山いるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine‚ don’t push yourself.\nYou have plenty of other idols to look after.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9999857583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、今がリズノワの正念場なんですよね\n必ず行きますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ this is a critical time for LizNoir.\nI’ll definitely go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5999857583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 145.3267203092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、期待せずに待ってるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah. I'll be waiting without expecting anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.3267203092,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3923.9982605000137,
          "startTime": 149.2507185697
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4257.33159379999,
          "startTime": 149.584051903
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.0007185697
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.0007185697
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……し、失礼します！　撮影は……！？\n……誰もいない。プールの方か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff… E-excuse me! How's the shoot…?!\n…There’s no one here. Are they at the pool?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.166660563,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5594.919816700013,
          "startTime": 161.7615803797
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.5115803797
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.5115803797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "撮影は無事に終わったわよ\n……貴方、本当に来たのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The shoot’s over.\n…You really came.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.566660563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……それなら良かった、です……\nでも……遅かったか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff… I’m glad to hear that…\nBut… I'm late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.6999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "まったくもう……\nそんなにまた、私の水着姿が見たかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my…\nDid you come all the way here just to see me in a swimsuit again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.2666646319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違いますよ！　いや、それはそれで失礼か……\nどう答えれば……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no! Wait‚ that would be rude…\nHow should I answer that…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.6999979653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、冗談よ。貴方の顔を見たら\nついホッとして、軽口が出ちゃったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I’m just kidding. Seeing your face\nmade me feel relieved and I just blurted it out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.0666646319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 199.0816784619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……その様子だと、いい仕事が出来たみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You seem to be in good spirits‚ so I guess the shoot went well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.1483380078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、まぁいろいろあったけどね\nなんとか乗り切ったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ well‚ there were a few things…\nbut we managed to pull through.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.7333343504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "例のプロデューサーも、本当はちゃんとした人だったし\nいろいろと、勉強にはなったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That producer… he actually turned out to be a decent guy‚\nand I learned a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.8333374021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 216.0645765065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……いえ、そうですよね\n莉央さんがいれば、LizNoirは安心です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… I mean‚ of course.\nWith you here‚ I have no worries about LizNoir‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.4000040688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "それはどうかしらね？　トップアイドルに向けて\n課題は山積みなのが、再認識出来たわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder about that? We’re still a long way from becoming top idols‚\nand there's still a lot we need to work on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.5000040688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 230.4907441218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "私も貴方を見習わないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to learn from you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.4907441218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 232.9716717481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "俺の？　どこを見習うんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Learn from me? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.9716717481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "周囲に配慮はしてるくせに、しっかり我を通すところ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re considerate of the people around you‚ but you also know how to stand your ground.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.6475447575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ？　そんなことありませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh? That’s not true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.2151863654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 244.1794382175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "嘘ね\n私達アイドルのことになると、一歩も引かないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a lie.\nWhen it comes to us idols‚ you never back down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.2333262124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 249.1349483729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか……我を通すのは弱さでもある\nとか言っておきながら、すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-is that so… I did say that being stubborn\ncan be a weakness… I apologize…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.3666595457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 258.0771475714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "……いいのよ。貴方はそれで\nこれからもよろしくね、頑固なマネージャーさん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It’s okay. You’re fine just the way you are.\nFrom now on too‚ I’ll be counting on you‚ stubborn manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.2333262124,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}